retweeted_text: Proud to stand on the House floor, with my friend @RepFinkenauer presiding, as the House unanimously approved two of my amendments to the disaster supplemental bill to increase funding for crucial programs Iowa needs to recover.

full_text: HR 2157, the Supplemental Appropriations Act, will provide billions in much-needed disaster funding, including $1.5 billion to repair damage caused by flooding & other disasters. Tune in here to watch me preside over the important debate: https://t.co/PQEsOqzMuK
